      "message": "Can we _not_ have this requirement?  This seems fairly poor as an implementation and I don\u0027t know why it would become a requirement.\n\nRedfish seems to use ResetType pretty consistently across all of these:\n\n```\n$ rg ResetType -t json -l                         \nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/Aggregate.v1_0_3.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/Application.v1_0_1.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/AggregationService.v1_0_3.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/MediaController.v1_3_2.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/Container.v1_0_1.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/Power.v1_7_3.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/Chassis.v1_28_0.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/Battery.v1_5_0.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/Drive.v1_22_0.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/NetworkAdapter.v1_14_0.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/Switch.v1_11_0.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/ComputerSystem.v1_28_0.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/Manager.v1_25_0.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/Memory.v1_24_0.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/Port.v1_19_0.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/PowerSupply.v1_7_0.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/Processor.v1_23_0.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/StorageController.v1_12_0.json\nredfish-core/schema/dmtf/json-schema/Storage.v1_22_0.json\n```\n\nWhy can\u0027t we make a single dbus interface for this?",
